Quickstrike turned his head to Stringtra. A grin broke through his mouth 
plate. "Oh, heh, sorry there. Ah was thinkin'. Pardon me." He walked off to

shoulder, looking briefly at the monitor she was in front of. He turned his 
head to the others. "Say' can't we's make uh doorway fer th' base? We's need 
somethin' fer jus' in case we's got uh barricade of firepower comin'. 
Otherwise we's needs a few guards t' watch out." He looked to Mantella and 
Stingtra.
